items.name: Wild Ones Wiki
items.title: Wild Ones Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Wild Ones Wiki!
items.desc: Most of you have probably heard of Facebook,Myspaceand Google+ Well you might have also heard that Facebook and Myspace have multiplayer games. Wild ones is one of them. Wild Ones is a multiplayer turn based shooting game which based on 'Worms'. You will start the game with a dog and as you continue throughout the game you have the option to get a rabbit, panda, monkey, cat, armadillo, chameleon, bat, hamster and many other Pets. There are also the 10 maps to play on and a bunch of weapons to use.

items.headline: Welcome to the JKT48 Home!
items.desc:
JKT48 is a international girlgroup based at Jakarta, Indonesia. This group is the first sister group of AKB48, an international girlgroup from Japan, from outside Japan. Come to our 'home' to check out more of JKT48!!!
Note: This wiki is using Indonesian language. We will try to make an English sometime ^_^
